! --- data plane ---
interface Loopback0
 ip address 59.59.59.59 255.255.255.255
interface Ethernet0/0
 description === to RT01 ===
 ip address 10.1.12.2 255.255.255.252
 no shutdown
interface Ethernet0/1
 description === to RT03 ===
 ip address 10.1.23.1 255.255.255.252
 no shutdown
ip access-list extended MONBLOCK
 deny udp any any eq snmp
 permit ip any any
interface Ethernet0/0
 ip access-group MONBLOCK in
router ospf 1
 router-id 59.59.59.59
 network 59.59.59.59 0.0.0.0 area 0
 network 10.1.12.0 0.0.0.3 area 0
 network 10.1.23.0 0.0.0.3 area 0
! --- SNMPv3 (NOC 監視標準) ---
snmp-server view MONVIEW iso included
snmp-server group MONGRP v3 priv read MONVIEW
snmp-server location CCNP-LAB
snmp-server user MONUSER MONGRP v3 auth sha CCNP-Auth-2026 priv aes 128 CCNP-Priv-2026
